<sect1 id="dir_26bcf0901e593cc8920ab58c2fc4c113_1autotoc_md252">
<title>helios::engine::runtime::spawn::policy::amount</title><para>Spawn amount providers for determining spawn quantities.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_26bcf0901e593cc8920ab58c2fc4c113_1autotoc_md253">
<title>Overview</title><para>This module provides SpawnAmountProvider implementations that determine how many entities should spawn when a rule&apos;s condition is satisfied.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_26bcf0901e593cc8920ab58c2fc4c113_1autotoc_md254">
<title>Key Classes</title><para><table rows="4" cols="2"><row>
<entry thead="yes"><para>Class  </para>
