</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>SpawnAmountProvider</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Abstract interface for calculating spawn quantity  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>FixedSpawnAmount</computeroutput>  </para>
